What algorithm should I use at start

When starting a campaign, it's recommended to use broad targeting and avoid layering options initially. This allows the algorithm to gather sufficient data during the Cold Start Period. Once you have enough data, you can edit your original ad set or launch a new ad set with more specific targeting. For more details, check out our tCPA Best Practices article.
